<br>
A link to this forum has been posted on UGoD, CiH, CT, TK, UC, WL, KC, FE, Max, and will be posted on as many guild's forums as we can find to make people aware of its existence. In addition, the clerics who are on the list are well aware of this board's existence, and should pass that information along to any cleric who visits Skyfire and inquires about the Ragefire camp. <br>
<br>
Hard feelings about the list has already arisen. If a cleric goes to Skyfire and finds a cleric on the list camping the spawn and takes the time to inquire, that cleric will be directed here, but will ultimately be the person responsible for getting his/her own name added to the list by sending in a simple e-mail.<br>
<br>
No cleric is ready to camp Ragefire if they do not have the Swirling Pearl. Taking the screen shot confirms that they are ready for the next step. <br>
<br>
I don't think there's anything prejudicial about the methods for getting your name onto the list. You can come here first, or go to Skyfire first and be told to come here. Either way, you'll make your way to the list. The ultimate aim is a civilized way of camping Ragefire that avoids hostility and bickering among people who would otherwise be friendly towards each other.<br>
<br>
We are just trying to support each other and try to get all the clerics who are ready a spot.<br>
