<br>
my 2 cents:<br>
<br>
Go and look on other servers where such lists exist for some time and you will find many new probems arise:<br>
<br>
1. A long list of like 100 clerics .. any new cleric has to wait 300 days to get a shot at RF even with very fast spawn time.<br>
2. There will always be people not respecting any form of list, and the server rules give them all right to do as they do, which is engage first with a force to take him down.<br>
3. How long is the 2nd in list going to wait before he moves in ? Example: First cleric falls asleep, noone else is around to call him on the phone. Is the 2nd cleric expected to wait 3 hours ? 6 hours ?<br>
4. If the 1st attempt fails, how many new shots does the cleric first in line get ? Does he get another ?<br>
<br>
So, just by those few points you see a little bit of the dilemma of a list. There are many more for sure which slipped my lazy mind.<br>
<br>
So in the end I think that this will not work.<br>
<br>
So long<br>
Nirtox O'Vindharr<br>
Oracle of Darkmoons<br>
